Package: shinyLoot
Title: An R Shiny Package for Managing Loot in Popular Tabletop RPG Games.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Robert",
           family = "Gilmore",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "robgilmore127@gmail.com")
Description: This package supplies the user with tools for managing loot for
popular tabletop RPG games.  While the package only currently supports Pathfinder
specifically, the first major release will be generalistic.  The primary tool
will be a group of functions for deploying a shiny app to use during game sessions
to keep up with loot.
